r"},{"pid":"fbb6f31a03b4f7fd80f01da8bb0fd3b7f95bfb22","tid":9600,"uid":10691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/001505_afa0242843207827d64d6973d9db3f09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F001505_afa0242843207827d64d6973d9db3f09.jpg&h=ec307fea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又黎發放負能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d4b32080b519aa8853a1e2bf8fa979537f6568","tid":9600,"uid":1259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>總會有人欣賞你既好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係時機未到，唔好灰心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會有架啦 花光心血仍難被記住<br />\n我已經22歳 重係一事無成 重係a0<br />\n我只不過鐘意一個肯同我心靈交流既女仔者<br />\n但係實程個個女仔都只係玩鳩你<br />\n<br />\n係呢一年我最學識既一樣野就係<br />\n原來佢生日同你出街食飯<br />\n再你生日同你出街食飯<br />\n到最後居然係連普通朋友都不如<br />\n一定係我毒得濟唔識同女仔相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先22歲，大把青春啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點樣大把？根本就無青春<br />\n我完全預想唔到我既未來<br />\n我真無切切實實感覺唔到任何希望<br />\n<br />\n由細到大一直係咁 硬係差啲運 差啲緣份"},{"pid":"c2aa56da5af0ec4d87a83f280b865b3862a43087","tid":9600,"uid":1259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:17:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/001505_afa0242843207827d64d6973d9db3f09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F001505_afa0242843207827d64d6973d9db3f09.jpg&h=9e1e598d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又黎發放負能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我既負能量輻射大過核電廠爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7418dc088ad410299c0855f562f68f7bc1dfee14","tid":9600,"uid":7846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:20:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6b0ca597d78b79542373ece2b172cd27399936d","tid":9600,"uid":1259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:24:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大美人發表個人對愛情既睇法</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://photouploads.com/images/fcee38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Ffcee38.jpg&h=6da0063d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://photouploads.com/images/c20c92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fc20c92.jpg&h=d748343a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://photouploads.com/images/4e3e85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F4e3e85.jpg&h=6210bd8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://photouploads.com/images/b41850.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fb41850.jpg&h=c1881e49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://photouploads.com/images/86670d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F86670d.jpg&h=5dad27fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://photouploads.com/images/e6ec05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fe6ec05.jpg&h=db241ebc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘉欣笑既時候 個世界靜止左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 咁應該要點做？<br />\n放棄嗎"},{"pid":"cc408b3ba988b7937fae56ffc7e14a5147d6fe44","tid":9600,"uid":31925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:25:23.000Z","msg":"一睇到標題第一時間諗到<br />\n「但唔努力就一定冇」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a988301d0daeafd96b67d69e084983e8e7ed6030","tid":9600,"uid":1259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:26:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一睇到標題第一時間諗到<br />\n「但唔努力就一定冇」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我試過啦 試過好多次啦<br />\n我唔敢再試啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d854f9e0daefb5f6cb0f55d36b0775abeafa2b23","tid":9600,"uid":15877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:27:08.000Z","msg":"講出完整故事吧"},{"pid":"4b32cd14a07af767e6decf7efec6a3e5d9fba4bd","tid":9600,"uid":27380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:29:52.000Z","msg":"夾既根本唔洗做d咩"},{"pid":"ee5aaad9877119d7157a5e87af8b35bc15c491a1","tid":9600,"uid":1259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T00:28:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講出完整故事吧</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我依家講既係兩個人黎<br />\n第一個女仔係我中學個陣既同學黎<br />\n我一直都好鐘意佢<br />\n畢業之後個幾年都無搵佢/無藉口搵佢<br />\n岩岩畢業個陣都有聯絡<br />\n什至佢當其時會上我屋企用電腦做功課<br />\n但之後已經無再聯絡<br />\n<br />\n事隔幾年<br />\n今年六月係佢既生日<br />\n我就用呢個藉口約佢食飯見佢<br />\n丫又真係應承<br />\n個晚之後我想再借啲意約佢<br />\n但係佢唔再應邀或者推辭<br />\n又隔左一個月到我生日<br />\n今次佢誰動約我食飯<br />\n咁樣到底係乜野玩法<br />\n<br />\n個晚有句野我特別深刻<br />\n原來隱喻係真言黎<br />\n我：重有冇下次？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢：無下次架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢既笑容好似講笑咁款,實情係講緊真話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n從此之後就無再約過佢了<br />\nWhatsapps亦多以已讀不回黎回應你"},{"pid":"85f812c3880c6e0c92af9cf3a39b73bed0c0bbb8","tid":9600,"uid":1259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T00:29:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夾既根本唔洗做d咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時夾既都唔會有感情存在<br />\n佢無咁既心你做乜都無用"},{"pid":"c75791073bbcfd5be70c1348fd37e215f430ddad","tid":9600,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T00:31:25.000Z","msg":"你無未必可得返 但你可以變大隻仔wo 去操下啦"},{"pid":"fa771e45306f2359009dd5cbc8daec53ca35cc88","tid":9600,"uid":22535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T00:31:41.000Z","msg":"你講得無錯，強求無幸福"},{"pid":"0bf61f3bbb77d7c5e0a9543e07cafa5db31c316d","tid":9600,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T00:31:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你無未必可<span style=\"color: red;\">高</span>得返 但你可以變大隻仔wo 去操下啦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"3c1adaf3d6b7ffdf645bf10e79f3c48ab03e4570","tid":9600,"uid":1259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T00:38:43.000Z","msg":"自此之後我疊埋心水<br />\n今年轉左新工<br />\n同期有個女同事一齊入職<br />\n我同佢有傾有講<br />\n不過話題太局限於公事<br />\n<br />\n我覺得真人同whatsapp回應好大出入<br />\n前幾日突然間打電話搵我傾計<br />\n我開心到震<br />\n我已經好耐無試過同女仔傾計<br />\n大家都傾到唔想收線<br />\n但係whatsapp就好易用表情黎回應我黎end個話題<br />\n<br />\n最特別既係 我試過問佢幾時生日<br />\n佢話唔需要知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話好多人都唔知 但係知既就知 唔知既都無需要知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a82302f8008a9837b674360720b3ed8646cf5ab","tid":9600,"uid":1259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:14:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你講得無錯，強求無幸福</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家連求都無得求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}